race.comment: DUNREAL (5) justified the short quote when making very light work of his rivals here, second-up. Still improving and looks well-suited by the rise in trip. A promising type who can win again. ISUSPECTJEU (7) has built nicely this campaign and will appreciate the extra journey. The 3kg claim gets her in well and she can run a big race. FLAMING NAVY (3) is at peak fitness now and has the speed to cross and lead. Will prove tough to catch if left alone. LONGER ROUTE (1) was too bad to be true last start but his first two runs of the prep were full of merit. Worth forgiving. SPARKUP (2) benefits from weight relief with the 3kg claimer engaged and is another who will give himself every chance up on speed.
